    {
        "url": "/quotes/bradley_a_smith_516376",
        "quote": "Incumbents don't like it, but political competition is a good thing. Incumbents usually outspend challengers by better than 3 to 1. Super PACs, which tend to support challengers, have nullified some of this advantage.",
