        "url": "/quotes/bradley_a_smith_516377",
        "quote": "With super PACs, we've seen voter turnout go up; interest in elections rise; and the number of competitive races increase. The campaigns of 2010 and 2012 have been more issue-oriented than their predecessors, not less.",
